data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! Income-producing property! This listing is for a full duplex, 517 & 521.  Each unit has 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths and is leased for $1550 to long-term tenants.  517 is leased thru 10.2024 and 521 is leased thru 4.2024.  The property features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a fenced backyard.  The roof was replaced in 2022.  Located on a quiet cul de sac and is surrounded by single-family homes.  Easy Access To Schools, Shopping And Metroplex. This a great opportunity for two-income properties under one roof!
